metadata.description: In honor of the momentous sale of the artwork "The Goose" by Dimitri Cherniak wich was sold for 6.2 million, we have decided to launch a special edition of CryptoSushis to commemorate this incredible milestone in the NFT world. This edition is so special that only one will exist, ensuring that the collector who acquires it will hold a unique piece of NFT history in their hands.
metadata.name: The Goose Sushi #68 #1/1
